60
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:41,140
Treat us to a big meal
with the prize money!

61
00:02:41,310 --> 00:02:42,400
That's a must.

62
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:43,960
Why are you always thinking about food?

63
00:02:44,350 --> 00:02:45,520
I just love food. What?

64
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,720
You only think about studying!

65
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,520
I… I…

66
