76
00:03:08,190 --> 00:03:09,190
Xiao Han, Happy Birthday!

77
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:11,080
Xiao Han, Happy Birthday!

78
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,150
Happy Birth…

79
