for dinner.

99
00:03:43,910 --> 00:03:44,750
- Sounds good.
- Great!

100
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:45,620
Set for the sixth.

101
00:03:45,620 --> 00:03:46,780
- Are you sure?
- No problem!

102
00:03:46,780 --> 00:03:48,680
- Settled?
- Everyone has to come, on the sixth.

103
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:50,120
See you all on the sixth!

104
00:03:52,770 --> 00:03:54,920
Qian Jiayue told us that

105
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:56,640
even though the celebration is later,

106
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:58,350
