107
00:03:58,520 --> 00:04:00,190
So, she asked us

108
00:04:00,190 --> 00:04:02,150
to prepare a card for you in advance.

109
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:03,680
The card comes first,

110
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:05,870
