114
00:04:11,540 --> 00:04:13,520
Higher the expectation,
greater the disappointment.

115
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:15,290
You don't need to
prepare anything special.

116
00:04:15,290 --> 00:04:16,640
If everyone does well in the finals

117
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:17,510
and enjoys the vacation,

118
00:04:17,510 --> 00:04:19,230
