143
00:05:18,270 --> 00:05:19,110
Honey.

144
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,640
Honey,

145
00:05:20,690 --> 00:05:22,430
do you think this outfit
looks good on me?

146
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:24,000
You look great in anything.

147
00:05:25,140 --> 00:05:26,120
I'll talk about it later.

148
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,800
At home,

149
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,920
don't dress like a siren.

150
00:05:31,190 --> 00:05:33,680
Help Qian Kang with some chores.

151
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:35,560
Got it, Mom.

152
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,440
Mom,

153
00:05:46,510 --> 00:05:48,240
