156
00:05:53,430 --> 00:05:54,510
Oh, you're exercising?

157
00:05:54,510 --> 00:05:56,070
It looks just like dancing.

158
00:05:59,070 --> 00:06:00,680
What do you want?

159
00:06:03,390 --> 00:06:04,230
Mom,

160
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,440
I remember

161
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:07,040
Chen Jianguo

162
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:10,270
gave you an Omega watch,

163
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,950
but I never see you wear it.

164
00:06:12,950 --> 00:06:14,020
What are you trying to say?

165
00:06:15,510 --> 00:06:16,790
In a few days,

166
00:06:16,790 --> 00:06:19,100
the old comrades from the countryside
are having a reunion.

167
00:06:19,100 --> 00:06:20,160
Mom, you don't know…

168
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,630
- they're all dressed up...
- I know.

169
00:06:21,870 --> 00:06:23,480
You want to show off

170
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:24,320
the watch

171
00:06:24,330 --> 00:06:25,600
in front of your old comrades,

172
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,440
right?

173
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,440
Mom,

174
00:06:27,510 --> 00:06:28,560
since you don't wear it,

175
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,600
can I borrow it for a bit?

176
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,520
Chen Xiu'e,

177
00:06:35,950 --> 00:06:38,800
when you meet your old comrades,

178
00:06:39,190 --> 00:06:41,360
why not focus on your comradeship,

179
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:44,000
remembering the hardships
you went through?

180
00:06:44,700 --> 00:06:45,540
Seriously,

181
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:46,680
it wasn't easy,

182
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:47,920
it's precious.

183
00:06:48,870 --> 00:06:50,070
What are you doing now?

184
00:06:50,390 --> 00:06:51,480
Showing off

185
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:53,360
a luxury watch

186
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,430
and acting rich?

187
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,390
Honestly, you're damaging

188
00:06:57,500 --> 00:07:00,510
the revolutionary spirit
between comrades!

189
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:01,920
I won't lend it to you.

190
00:07:03,420 --> 00:07:06,160
I won't support your

191
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,000
vanity!

192
00:07:07,270 --> 00:07:08,510
Vanity?

193
00:07:08,510 --> 00:07:10,600
I just wanted to
borrow your watch for a bit.

194
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,680
Why make it such a big deal,

195
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,600
holding a struggle session.

196
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,620
- Yes, a struggle session.
- Fine, I don't need it.

197
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,000
I don't want it!

198
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,750
The computer's broken!

199
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,680
The millennium bug!

200
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,000
Honey, is it broken?

201
00:07:22,910 --> 00:07:23,830
Oh, the computer.

202
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:24,690
No, no, it's not that.

203
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,750
I'm mopping the floor,

204
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:27,270
I accidentally knocked into this,

205
00:07:27,270 --> 00:07:28,190
and it fell down.

206
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:29,030
See?

207
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,920
It should be fine.

208
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:31,760
Let me take a look.

209
00:07:40,950 --> 00:07:41,790
What's this?

210
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,640
Go out.

211
00:07:44,310 --> 00:07:45,150
Put it back.

212
00:07:45,270 --> 00:07:46,110
Out.

213
00:07:46,270 --> 00:07:47,510
- Don't read it.
- Out.

214
00:07:50,870 --> 00:07:51,920
Close the door.

215
00:08:10,190 --> 00:08:11,120
It's in English.

216
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:12,670
The drawing's really nice.

217
00:08:15,950 --> 00:08:16,800
Baby,

218
00:08:17,430 --> 00:08:19,070
I'm not reading your diary.

219
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:21,510
I just wanted to check

220
00:08:21,510 --> 00:08:23,390
if your handwriting's improved,

221
00:08:23,830 --> 00:08:25,310
and if your writing's good.

222
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:28,000
I'm not trying to read the content.

223
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:28,840
Right?

224
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,720
I almost made a mistake again.

225
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,160
Baby,

226
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,440
I didn't read it.

227
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,550
I'm putting it back now.

228
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:44,560
Coming!

229
00:08:45,750 --> 00:08:46,590
Kang.

230
00:08:47,510 --> 00:08:48,350
Qiming.

231
00:08:48,670 --> 00:08:49,510
