243
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,360
You look so elegant!

244
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:10,540
This color looks great on you!

245
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:11,680
Zhang Qiming.

246
00:09:11,740 --> 00:09:12,750
You bought so many things!

247
00:09:12,750 --> 00:09:13,610
Spending money on you

248
00:09:13,610 --> 00:09:14,600
makes me happy!

249
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:16,120
No need. You're wasting too much money.

250
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,440
Not at all. Where's Jiayue?

251
00:09:18,150 --> 00:09:20,320
She's at Chen Mo's place studying.

252
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,120
Your son's there too.

253
00:09:22,630 --> 00:09:24,640
That little imp finally decided
to study hard, huh?

254
00:09:24,870 --> 00:09:25,710
That's good.

255
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:28,120
Xiao Han's helping him study.

256
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:30,760
Aren't you happy? Someone's helping
take care of your son for free.

257
00:09:30,990 --> 00:09:33,080
We're family.
Naturally we help each other out.

258
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,200
That's hilarious!

259
00:09:34,270 --> 00:09:35,750
