263
00:09:46,270 --> 00:09:47,720
Auntie, stop joking about it.

264
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,720
She's really a mood killer.

265
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,750
That marriage exists in name only.

266
00:09:53,750 --> 00:09:54,600
You're really annoying

267
00:09:54,610 --> 00:09:55,550
